{"tid":1937694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"入境處講大話? 定機管局犯法助他人非法入境?","createTime":"2020-03-22T05:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T13:48:33.000Z","uid":123774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"13116d895676238bccea9443b07f1181ecb0d396","tid":1937694,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T05:39:30.000Z","msg":"入境處數字話得少過50個大陸人經機場入境<br />\n咁前幾日示威然後機場車去深圳灣係乜黎?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過千中國人在機場禁區非法集會示威，涉嫌暴動，入境處竟然跪低答應訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1935617\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1935617</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g5vMUk8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg5vMUk8.jpg&h=a770a54c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有片有真相: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/Bdp3w_ZXn38\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBdp3w_ZXn38&d=HaOdbOSPDN3vR1kWeckjcA1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=ae153a0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Bdp3w_ZXn38</a><br />\n<br />\n大陸入境人數: <a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/message_from_us/stat3.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fmessage_from_us%2Fstat3.htm&d=HaOdbOSPDN3vR1kWeckjcA1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=e628d3d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/message_from_us/stat3.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n3月19日 37<br />\n3月20日 44<br />\n3月21日 43"},{"pid":"1dac40703e23075f983aa77728c3bfbc096e4335","tid":1937694,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T05:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59787d01594c446536c42b3f2aca72529ba304b0","tid":1937694,"uid":123774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T05:43:11.000Z","msg":"經陸路安排巴士送走深圳灣唔當入境?<br />\n係咪打算呢個係以後長遠安排?!<br />\n<br />\n如果全世界都要強制14日隔離<br />\n點解支那有違法特別安排<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x